  "keyFeatures": [
    "IKEv1 and IKEv2 protocol support for IPsec VPN tunnels",
    "swanctl command-line tool for managing VPN connections",
    "VICI (Versatile IKE Control Interface) for daemon control and monitoring",
    "Comprehensive PKI toolchain (pki) for certificate and CRL management",
    "Extensive plugin architecture with 70+ plugins for crypto, EAP, kernel backends",
    "Support for EAP authentication methods (MD5, MSCHAPv2, TLS, PEAP, RADIUS)",
    "Virtual IP address pool management for roadwarrior clients",
    "TPM 2.0 Trusted Platform Module integration for secure key storage",
    "NetworkManager integration via charon-nm",
    "Android VPN client support",
    "High-availability (HA) clustering support"
  ],
